@Entity - specify class is a entity
@Table
@Id - primary key of the entity
@Column
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@Generated Value - define generation types ( AUTO / IDENTITY / SEQUENCE / TABLE )
        IDENTITY - auto increment
        SEQUENCE - create a sequence table contains next value for the increment
        AUTO - database platform eka most suitable generation type eka select karagannawa
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@Transient - need to keep a attribute in a entity but not add them to tables
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@CreationTimestamp - provide real time date and time to a table
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------